To win $3.5 million you must follow these simple steps:

1.- Select the preset of your choice.
2.- Start the heist on the 3rd preparation board.
3.- In the heist setup screen, you and your team should ready up.
4.- In the vault, only you should grab the chosen item to steal.
5.- Complete the heist and receive $3.5 million.
6.- (OPTIONAL) Repeat every 30 minutes.

(!) Your percentage should not exceed 60%
(!) Other players' percentage should be 147%
(!) If you modify anything in the heist setup screen, you won't receive the $3.5 million upon completing the heist.

Ignoring the above will reset everything.

VIEW_SQUAD_SPAWN_VEHICLE_CATCH_UP_TOOLTI:
Will spawn the mobile squad behind the target with identical velocity if applicable.
Only for squads with a vehicle.
VIEW_STAT_EDITOR_DATE_TOOLTIP:
year month day hour minute second millisecond
Example: 2022 1 17 21 34 55
VIEW_STAT_EDITOR_PACKED_STAT_INDEX_HELP: Index: enter two numbers to represent a range (31786 32786)
VIEW_STAT_EDITOR_WARNING: Be aware of stat limits, use with caution, modifying some stats are risky.
VIEW_VEHICLE_CONTROL_RENDER_DISTANCE_ON_: Will display the distance on the controlled vehicle.
VIEW_VEHICLE_CONTROL_SHOW_VEHICLE_INFO_D: Shows the current vehicle health and the amount of passengers in the vehicle.
VIEW_VEHICLE_CONTROL_USE_ANIMATIONS_DESC:
Will use animations for several vehicle operations such as:
toggling lights, opening/closing doors and entering seats.
VIEW_WEAPON_CUSTOM_GUN_ONLY_FIRES_WHEN_T: Custom Gun only fires when the weapon is out
VIEW_WEAPON_WEAPON_HOTKEYS_TOOLTIP:
This will select the next weapon in the hotkey list.
The first weapon in the list is the first weapon it will select, then the second is the one it will select after and so on.
After the end of the list, it will wrap back to the first weapon.
WALK_UNDERWATER_DESC: You can walk on the Bikini Bottom floor.
WIZARD_ALL_DESC: Start The Wizard's Ruin video game in fullscreen for the whole session.
YOU_HAVE_BEEN_KICKED: You have been kicked by the host
